Suggests: croc
Maintainer: Shuki Vaknin <shuki@linux-hosting.co.il>
Homepage: https://git.linux-hosting.co.il/shukivaknin/gniza4linux
Description: Linux backup manager with web dashboard and TUI
 Gniza is a backup manager for Linux that provides incremental backups
 using rsync with hardlink deduplication. Features include a web dashboard,
 terminal UI, scheduled backups, and support for local, SSH, S3, and
 Google Drive sources and destinations.
